properties.text: ???: "This is a Spirit Orb.... It is one of the more common enemies... Be careful... You must defeat every enemy to proceed..."
???: "A Necromancer has appeared!! Be careful! It can attack from a far! Take this powerups!"
???: "A portal... How strange... Proceed with caution. I sense an evil presence and dark magicks radiating from within the portal..."
???: "This is a Skill Power. Collect this."

Tutorial Voice: "Use W/Space to jump. Use A/D to move left/right. Use the Number Keys, 1 through 7, to select your magic attack type. Use Q or LMB to Magic Attack. Use RMB to Melee Attack. MMB to fire an Arrow (note the limited numbers). To review controls info, hold P."
???: "This are pass-through platforms. Jump to get through them."
You need to wait for cooldown!
???: "I told you, that is a question for another time."
